MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-673. Fahnbulleh v. Strahan.

Franklin County, No. 93AP-135. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective August 30, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
